empires.name: Federation
empires.desc:
Founded in 2161 on Earth, the United Federation of planets spans thousands of
lightyears and 150+ member planets.
Traditionally lead by a President, the Federation has been without one since
 SD 86621.568754 (2409) when President Armitage was assassinated.

Since then, it has been loosely run by the ellusive Daystrom Institute (rumor)

empires.name: Klingon
empires.desc:
Founded in the 9th century by QeylIS (Kahless) the Unforgettable the Empire
spans several thousand light years around it's homeworld of Qo'noS. In ancient
times the Empire was ran as a dictatorship by the Emperor, however, in this age
it is governed by the High Council and the Qang (Chancellor). The role of
Emperor is retained as more of a religious figurehead, rather than
direct government control.

The Empire employs advancedphase-disruptor technology and cloaking devices in
every ship of the Imperial Navy, giving them an edge in any combat situation.

empires.name: GFA
empires.desc: The Galactic Ferengi Alliance is a sparse cluster of planets, centered around Ferenganor, which is colonized by the Ferengi and governed by the Ferengi Commerce Authority (or FCA). As an intensely capitalist society, the alliance is inclusive of most races which are capable of turning a profit.
